ISLAMABAD, Sep 30 (APP): Prime Minister Shehbaz Sharif on Friday expressed deep grief and sorrow over the death of the mother of CEO of Daily Express Ijaz ul Haq.
The prime minister in his condolence message prayed for the departed soul to rest in peace and for grant of patience to the bereaved family.
